• Search your library and/or graveyard for a card named Severum, reveal it, and put it onto the battlefield. If you search your library this way, shuffle.
• Search your library and/or graveyard for a card named Gravitum, reveal it, and put it onto the battlefield. If you search your library this way, shuffle.
